⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Starscourge Radahn
node ER · ER · ⟦Starscourge Radahn:ER:bc3969⟧

WHO   — Starscourge Radahn — the general who held back the stars
WHAT  — Mightiest demigod general, son of Radagon and Rennala, who halted the stars in their courses.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: Caelid and the stalemate of Aeonia  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — While he stood, the stars and the fate they govern were frozen; his fall lets them move again, and a falling star opens the way to Nokron.
HOW   — Learned gravity magic to ride his beloved undersized horse Leonard, and turned that strength against the heavens themselves.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The stars stood still because one warrior refused to yield — and moved again only when he was given a warrior's death.

